Планируем посмотреть на major arc of mammals and check: Грубо MajorArc с 6000 по 16000 We compare number of DI...I.D with number of D.I...ID in all mammalian species and we expect:

  1. N(DI...I.D on heavy strand) < N(D.I...ID on heavy strand)
  2. this difference should be more pronounced in long-lived mammals
  3. for strong (long) repeats

N(DI...I.D on heavy strand) << N(D.I...ID on heavy strand)

Long Summary table D1 (interval 1) I (interval 2) I (interval 3) D:

SpeciesName

  • DirectRepeat1.Motiv

  • DirectRepeat1.Length

  • DirectRepeat1.Location

  • LengthOfInterval1

  • InvertedRepeat1.Motiv

  • InvertedRepeat1.Length

  • InvertedRepeat1.Location

  • LengthOfInterval2

  • InvertedRepeat2.Motiv

  • InvertedRepeat2.Length

  • InvertedRepeat2.Location

  • LengthOfInterval3

  • DirectRepeat2.Motiv

  • DirectRepeat2.Length

  • DirectRepeat2.Location

  • LengthOfInterval1 <= 1000 bp

  • LengthOfInterval2 > 500 bp # large scale deletions

  • LengthOfInterval3 <= 1000 bp

DIMENSIONALITY: (200 mammalian species X hundreds DIID for each species) ~ 40000 rows

Смотрим Fragility (соотношение DI...I.D и D.I...ID) при разных параметрах

Функция применеяющая параметры¶

In [54]:
def dandi(area, fi,se,th,fo,loi1,loi2,loi3, real):
    # if  i[2] - (d[2]+d[4]-1) <= loi1 and i[3] - (i[2]+i[4]-1) > loi2 and d[3] - (i[3]+i[4]-1) <= loi3:  
    if area == 'min':
        di = data[(((data[fi[0]] + data[fi[1]] - 1 < 6000) & (data[se[0]] + data[se[1]] - 1 < 6000)) | ((data[fi[0]] > 16000) & (data[se[0]] > 16000))) & 
                  (((data[th[0]] + data[th[1]] - 1 < 6000) & (data[fo[0]] + data[fo[1]] - 1 < 6000)) | ((data[th[0]] > 16000) & (data[fo[0]] > 16000))) & 
                  ((data[fi[0]] + data[fi[1]] <= data[se[0]]) & (data[th[0]] + data[th[1]] - 1 < data[fo[0]])) & 
                  ((data[se[0]] - (data[fi[0]] + data[fi[1]] - 1) >= loi1[0]) & (data[se[0]] - (data[fi[0]] + data[fi[1]] - 1) <= loi1[1])) & 
                  ((data[th[0]] - (data[se[0]] + data[se[1]] - 1) >= loi2[0]) & (data[th[0]] - (data[se[0]] + data[se[1]] - 1) <= loi2[1])) & 
                  ((data[fo[0]] - (data[th[0]] + data[th[1]] - 1) >= loi3[0]) & (data[fo[0]] - (data[th[0]] + data[th[1]] - 1) <= loi3[1])) & 
                  (data['RealDel'] == real)]
    elif area == 'maj':
        di = data[((data[fi[0]] >= 6000) & (data[se[0]] >= 6000) & (data[th[0]] >= 6000) & (data[fo[0]] >= 6000) & 
                   (data[fi[0]] + data[fi[1]] - 1 <= 16000) & (data[se[0]] + data[se[1]] - 1 <= 16000) & 
                   (data[th[0]] + data[th[1]] - 1 <= 16000) & (data[fo[0]] + data[fo[1]] - 1 <= 16000)) & 
                  ((data[fi[0]] + data[fi[1]] <= data[se[0]]) & (data[th[0]] + data[th[1]] - 1 < data[fo[0]])) & 
                  ((data[se[0]] - (data[fi[0]] + data[fi[1]] - 1) >= loi1[0]) & (data[se[0]] - (data[fi[0]] + data[fi[1]] - 1) <= loi1[1])) & 
                  ((data[th[0]] - (data[se[0]] + data[se[1]] - 1) >= loi2[0]) & (data[th[0]] - (data[se[0]] + data[se[1]] - 1) <= loi2[1])) & 
                  ((data[fo[0]] - (data[th[0]] + data[th[1]] - 1) >= loi3[0]) & (data[fo[0]] - (data[th[0]] + data[th[1]] - 1) <= loi3[1])) & 
                  (data['RealDel'] == real)]
    return di.shape[0]

import seaborn as sns
# Извлеките столбцы для построения графика
plot_data = nums[['dii.d_real', #'G', 
                      'd.iid_real', 
                      'loi1start', 
                      'loi1end', 
                      'loi2start', 
                      'loi2end', 
                      'loi3start', 
                      'loi3end']]

# Функция для расчета коэффициента корреляции между двумя столбцами
def corr_func(x, y, **kwargs):
    r = np.corrcoef(x, y)[0][1]
    ax = plt.gca()
    ax.annotate("r = {:.2f}".format(r),
                xy=(.2, .8), xycoords=ax.transAxes,
                size = 20)

# Создайте объект pairgrid
grid = sns.PairGrid(data = plot_data)

# Вверху - диаграмма рассеяния
grid.map_upper(plt.scatter, color = 'red', alpha = 0.6)

# Диагональ - это гистограмма
grid.map_diag(plt.hist, color = 'red', edgecolor = 'black')

# Внизу график корреляции и плотности.
grid.map_lower(corr_func);
grid.map_lower(sns.kdeplot, cmap = plt.cm.Reds)

# Название всего графика
plt.suptitle('Pairs Plot', size = 36, y = 1.02);

dfperc = df
def realproc(com):
    global dfperc
    dfperc = dfperc.with_columns( 
        pl.struct(
            [com + '_unreal',com +'_real']
        ).map_elements(
            lambda x:  (    
                int( x[com +'_real'] / ( (x[com + '_unreal'] + x[com +'_real']) / 100) )
                if x[com +'_real']>0 else 0
            )   
        ).alias(
            com+'_realperc'
            
        )
        
    )
    

realproc('dii.d')
realproc('d.iid')
realproc('diid')
realproc('d.ii.d')
realproc('idd.i')
realproc('i.ddi')
realproc('iddi')
realproc('i.dd.i')
realproc('idi.d')
realproc('i.did')
realproc('idid')
realproc('i.di.d')
realproc('did.i')
realproc('d.idi')
realproc('didi')
realproc('d.id.i')
dfperc
